markdown: PROGRAM FOR DR. ROBERT SHANK 19 Wednesday 12:00 - To São Paulo by VASP. 13:15 - Arrive São Paulo - to Hotel Excelsior - lunch there or nearby 14:30 - To Escola Paulista de Medicina - Dean Jose Maria de Freitas - basic sciences. 20 Thursday 09:00 - Escola Paulista de Medicina - Complete basic sciences, if necessary, in forenoon (Microbiology, Pharmacology, Bio-chemistry are principal RF interests). Rest of day with clinical medicine. 21 Friday 09:00 - To Escola Paulista de Medicina - Entire day in Clinical Medicine. 22 Saturday 09:00 - To Escola Paulista de Medicina, with Zerbini and Decourt in forenoon. Afternoon free for sightseeing or further visits as desired. 23 Sunday - Free - Could go to Ribeirão Preto if Zeferino Vaz desires. 24 Monday 07:00 - To Ribeirão Preto by VASP. Buy ticket after consulting with Dr. Zeferino Vaz; he may buy ticket for RES, and will wither accompany RES to Ribeirão Preto or send someone. 8:15 - Arrive Ribeirão Preto - Hotel Umuarama - rest of day in basic science departments. 25 Tuesday - Ribeirão Preto - Preventive Medicine, Clinica Medicine, etc. 26 Wednesday - Ribeirão Preto - As for Tuesday 27 Thursday - Return to São Paulo 28 Friday - São Paulo to Lima **** Source: https://www.industrydocuments.ucsf.edu/docs/pgxg0227
